@startuml
' @id(CMP-MAP-SKILL)
' @desc(CMP-MAP-SKILL, "The /mdd-map skill definition at .claude/skills/mdd-map/SKILL.md — the agent-executed instructions that derive the current view from code. As of cycle 0020 its workflow includes a mockup-authoring step (3a): whole-repo scope auto-includes current-side MCK- Salt mockups for discovered UI apps (UIC ids mirroring data-testids); feature/module scope keeps mockups opt-in. No Rust changes; the deterministic mdd-validate gate enforces the MCK-/UIC- contract rules the step satisfies.")
title MDD map skill — mockup-aware ownership (current)

actor "Developer / Agent" as Dev

component "/mdd-map SKILL.md\n(CMP-MAP-SKILL)\n.claude/skills/mdd-map" as Map
component "current/<kind>/*.puml\n(5 UML kinds)" as Uml
component "current/mockups/*.puml\n(MCK-, whole-repo scope)" as Mck
component "mdd validate\n(deterministic gate)" as Validate

Dev --> Map : /mdd-map <scope>
Map --> Uml : author use-cases (+ kinds on request)
Map --> Mck : whole-repo -> author mockups for UI apps
Map --> Validate : hand off

note bottom of Mck
  Whole-repo scope auto-includes mockups; feature/module
  scope keeps them opt-in. UIC ids mirror app data-testids.
end note
@enduml
